title: Olena Zelenska Took Part in the Opening of a Kitchen Factory in the Kharkiv Region — Official website of the President of Ukraine
snippet: News · President's wife · 11 December 2025 - 20:18 · In the Kharkiv region, First Lady of Ukraine Olena Zelenska took part in the launch of a kitchen factory opened as part of the school nutrition reform.

title: All news — Official web site of the President of Ukraine
snippet: Since the beginning of 2025, more than two million children in Ukraine have been provided with free hot meals. This was announced by First Lady Olena Zelenska as she summed up this year’s results of implementing the school nutrition reform.

title: The Olena Zelenska Foundation Opened the First “12–21” Youth Space in Bila Tserkva — Official website of the President of Ukraine
snippet: News · President's wife · 12 December 2025 - 21:09 · The first youth space of the “12–21” network, created by the Olena Zelenska Foundation, has opened in Bila Tserkva. This is a barrier-free center designed for leisure, peer-to-peer ...

title: Olena Zelenska Took Part in the Annual Educational Conference “Serpneva-2025” — Official website of the President of Ukraine
snippet: First Lady of Ukraine Olena Zelenska took part in the annual educational conference “Serpneva-2025,” organized by the Ministry of Education and Science.

title: In Japan, Olena Zelenska Took Part in Ukraine’s National Day at EXPO 2025 — Official website of the President of Ukraine
snippet: First Lady of Ukraine Olena Zelenska took part in Ukraine’s National Day at EXPO 2025, held in Osaka.
